Interface Summary
Contact A contact is a person we are making business with or may do in the future.
ContactManager A class to manage contacts and meetings.
FutureMeeting A meeting to be held in the future
IdStore Used for storing the static idAssigner variables from the Meeting and Contact classes so that the ID values are not lost when the program is closed.
Meeting A class to represent meetings Meetings have unique IDs, scheduled date and a list of participating contacts
PastMeeting A meeting that was held in the past.
 

Class Summary
